title: AXL-DC - Back In Lack 2016 ak
description:
AXL-DC - Back In Lack 2016 ak

Well now the tour has resumed and Brian is not around and Axl is the frontman for better or worse. I went through a selection of 50 tracks taken from all different times of the band Bon Tracks And Brian. And I decided to make this and float it to you guys.
I  know the original recording is not a sound board rip. I can hear the fans better than I want. But this is what it is if you want more from the source content tell me cause this is more than enough for me and the 50 was to much.
